        "description": {
            "value": "<p>At 18th level, you&rsquo;ve learned to command the elements to summon a fierce storm in a 30-foot radius around you. As an action, you can gain the following benefits for 1 minute:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain a flying speed equal to your walking speed.</li>\n<li>You have resistance to energy, lightning, and necrotic damage.</li>\n<li>Whenever a hostile creature enters this radius or starts its turn there, it takes 10 lightning damage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This effect ends early if you are incapacitated or die. Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
